    <briefdescription>
<para>A <ref refid="classDali_1_1LongPressGesture" kindref="compound">LongPressGesture</ref> is emitted when the user touches and holds the screen with the stated number of fingers. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This gesture can be in one of two states, when the long-press gesture is first detected: <ref refid="namespaceDali_1a1c7153324546349d2a60223f6e1895afa17130e6c806885e23770df1519b18eb7" kindref="member">GestureState::STARTED</ref> and when the long-press gesture ends: <ref refid="namespaceDali_1a1c7153324546349d2a60223f6e1895afa2c616b2713e2e0aed04b4c4752c88133" kindref="member">GestureState::FINISHED</ref>.</para>
<para>Long press gesture finishes when all touches have been released.</para>
<para>@SINCE_1_9.28 <simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="classDali_1_1LongPressGestureDetector" kindref="compound">LongPressGestureDetector</ref> </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
